OL,5,G2235 STV News; Weather
OL,6,G2250 Bradley & Barney Walsh: Breaking
OL,7,G     Dad
OL,8,     FThe duo head to the outback, where
OL,9,     Fthey meet a group of farmers and
OL,10,     Fhelp them muster their cattle. The
OL,11,     Fpair then make a pit stop at a
OL,12,     Flocal bar and take part in a pub
OL,13,     Fquiz. The next day it's
OL,14,     Fcompetition time as father and son
OL,15,     Fgo head-to-head in a race on
OL,16,     Flawnmowers. Their trip takes them
OL,17,     Ftowards the coast and the
OL,18,     Fbeautiful Whitsundays, where a
OL,19,     Ftrip on a super yacht awaits them.
OL,20,     FHowever, they won't be doing any
OL,21,     Frelaxing, because they're working
OL,22,     Fon board
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
