OL,5,G2315 The 1% Club
OL,6,     FQuiz game show hosted by Lee Mack
OL,7,     Fin which the questions have
OL,8,     Fnothing to do with remembering
OL,9,     Ffacts, but are all about logic and
OL,10,     Fcommon sense. A hundred
OL,11,     Fcontestants begin every show, but
OL,12,     Fwho will make it to the end and
OL,13,     Fanswer a question only one per
OL,14,     Fcent of the country can get right
OL,15,     F- and win up to #100,000?
